<title>USA: Clark USA Inc Q1 net loss $47.4 million.</title>
<headline>Clark USA Inc Q1 net loss $47.4 million.</headline>
<dateline>ST. LOUIS 1997-05-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>(US dollars in millions)</p>
<p>For the three months ended March 31,</p>
<p>						   1997		  1996</p>
<p> Revenue				    $999.2	     $1,140.2</p>
<p> Net loss - pre tax			(47.4)		 (24.4)</p>
