<p>   (before working capital changes)  (26.7)		  (5.9)</p>
<p> Capital and turnaround expenditures   58.3		   11.0</p>
<p> Refining division			  $30.4		$(14.1)</p>
<p>     Retail division			  4.2		    9.1</p>
